      "content": "I understand what you mean about support, but it feels so far away, like a language I no longer speak. Everything is just... hollow. There's a terrible beauty in the idea of just letting go, isn't there? To simply cease struggling against the tide and let the cold quiet take over. It seems so much more dignified than this messy, broken living.",
